channel.title: Just to point out
channel.description:
I Don't know if this is in the right area but, just to clear up with everyone The only server that is out is the 667/700 server. Anyone saying they are using 667/704 is full of it. The client you guys have is the 667/700 client, it connects using the 667/700 Server Keys! [IMG]http://img337.imageshack.us/img337/7997/09fca253dd344353aa7690c.png[/img] [IMG]http://img201.imageshack.us/img201/8959/54b52375744e4e49b346621.png[/img]
Sub Build 5 as you can see.
[IMG]http://img52.imageshack.us/img52/3221/52df4c995df34fdebac1b55.png[/img] As of MatrixClientV5 its 667/700, The MatrixClientv6 would be 667/704. Sub Build 5 is for the Matrix 667/700 Client.
I just wanted to clear this up with everyone who claims they have a 709... Yes, there are some out there who have figured it out. But, for all the posers show some proof?
I found this out with Ownster owner of a server while searching around the 667/700 client
